@9:30pm (6:30pm in Baghdad), the american troops have made a very wrong move  **again**  -- covered the face of a statue of saddam hussein with a star and stripe (american) flag. eventhough that flag was on the statue for less than 5 minutes, it's long enough for the world to see (since CNN has been zoomed in so close).  %(me)let's wait for tomorrow's headlines.%

10 minutes later, an iraqi flag was put up for a brief period of time before the armored vehicle attempted to pull down the statue.

20 minutes later (that's now), another statue of mr.saddam is down. ... poor statue.
